[normal]“
[normal]We recommend that a White Paper be published, clarifying the Government’s objectives for all transport spending and the criteria it will use for deciding between different claims on the available resources”
[normal] – Recommendation 5, 
[normal]Transport and the Economy, Third Report of Session 2010-12, House of Commons Transport Committee 
[normal]http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201011/cmselect/cmtran/473/473.pdf
