[normal]“
[normal]The route exploits the natural lie of the land and runs alongside the motorway to 
[normal]minimise
[normal] environmental impact … within a corridor with an already dense infrastructure”
[normal] – The
[normal] New High Speed Turin - Milan 
[normal]Line, RFI 2005 
